CSS property<p><pre><code> overflow:hidden 
</code></pre>
...should just crop. <p>If the transition text-jump isn't too annoying, this might also be interesting:<p><pre><code> pre {overflow:hidden; padding:2px}
 pre:hover {overflow:auto}
</code></pre>
PRE blocks would be clipped until mouseover, when a scrollbar would appear if necessary (bumping following text down).
